Text: Is this a real CD rip or just the same old upconverted copy of the MySpace rip?

M:10 A:7
Sure it's better than the "Myspace rip", but seems like you had too aggressive setting for lowpass filter in your mp3 encoder?! The highest frequencies are missing.
Yeah, that's why I asked, it sounds really weird. Because I have a 192kbps rip of this album and it sounds slightly better than this 320kbps one.
